BH/BLASTRAGE


BH walks out of the cr chamber. He checks his armor and to make sure 
it polish. He then turns to BLASTRAGE. "I want my Damn energon cubes. 
Please contact Koga shuko And tell him I want my energon cubes"

BLASTRAGE jumps out of his chair and goes over to the com unit. he 
plays with a few button when he says into the com "Koga Shuko when
can 
 We get our Energon cubes?"
